interpretation: The "woman: bald" card is a symbol of transformation, liberation, and acceptance. The bald head represents a shedding of external appearances and societal expectations, allowing the true self to shine through. This card encourages embracing one's unique identity and letting go of any shame or insecurity surrounding physical appearance. It can also indicate a period of personal growth and self-discovery. Keywords associated with this card include: authenticity, confidence, self-love, acceptance, and change.
